main event: A UFO sighting of a spherical shaped object pulsating white light was reported in the Atlantic on December 9, 1963.
interesting points: The object was reported to have no red or green lights visible., The sighting was classified as military., Observation was noted to be of medium altitude and high speed., The conclusion was insufficient data for a thorough evaluation., Two observers, including an OOD and a lookout from USS Savage, sighted the object.
sighted object: spherical shaped object pulsating white light
witness description: OOD and lookout from USS Savage
